Author: cardigante
Text: This is trying to eat with my boyfriend. He’s a trained chef and makes everything with a ton of butter and oil and salt which makes it delicious but then he always has to serve me huge plates and bowls when I really want to just give myself like 1 tbs of rice or whatever it is. I’m like I WILL SERVE MYSELF THHAANKKK UUUu.
